<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Lalpa, khawvel Salhvakpa,
 Zie In ahin hung chengin;
 Zie maicham ahin ka kipieu,
 Nangin ei na pawm inla;
 Na Thagau Thiengtho vak lopi,
 Na lungsietna thu pha kha;
 Huihpi bang mutheilo mahleng,
 Dai kie bangin ei vukin.

[V2]
 2. Ziehi Na Ho-In a hung hii,
 Ei Dawngpa hung hi zingin;
 Kivawp zing di'n ei panpih in,
 Paucham lungthim ei pien la;
 Na aw nemin thu ei hilh in,
 Gilo kisikna hi hen;
 Lalpa, Na min lopina di'n,
 Sapchuomte hun zemhawih in.</lyrics>
<title>MORIAH</title>
<hymn_number>217</hymn_number>
</song>